Package net.minecraftforge.client.model.generators

Class BlockStateProvider

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.client.model.generators.BlockStateProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataProvider
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataGeneratorTest.BlockStates, NewModelLoaderTest.BlockStates, PistonEventTest.BlockStates, ScaffoldingTest.ScaffoldingBlockState
public abstract class BlockStateProvider extends Object implements DataProvider
Data provider for blockstate files. Extends BlockModelProvider so that blockstates and their referenced models can be provided in tandem.
